me feel uncomfortable, hey,

00:44:59.715 --> 00:45:01.760
can you think about
this way, maybe?

00:45:01.760 --> 00:45:07.650
What happens over time is you
change that behavior, and then

00:45:07.650 --> 00:45:11.770
the psychological trick where
you decide how you want to feel

00:45:11.770 --> 00:45:13.800
and then the mind
justifies it, you

00:45:13.800 --> 00:45:16.460
decide that you want to
feel like not doing this,

00:45:16.460 --> 00:45:18.520
because the social cost is less.

00:45:18.520 --> 00:45:22.260
And then your attitudes
slowly start to change.

00:45:22.260 --> 00:45:24.400
