00:48:32.840 --> 00:48:34.920
is part of the problem.

00:48:34.920 --> 00:48:38.060
But I think if you want
to look at it more deeply,

00:48:38.060 --> 00:48:40.980
there are all these
unconscious messages.

00:48:40.980 --> 00:48:46.090
They've been telling
boys, now 35-year-old men,

00:48:46.090 --> 00:48:48.430
that games are their space.

00:48:48.430 --> 00:48:50.130
It's not women's space.

00:48:50.130 --> 00:48:52.990
It happens in all
these subtle ways.

00:48:52.990 --> 00:48:56.580
Princess Peach is always waiting
to be rescued in the castle.

00:48:56.580 --> 00:49:01.850
When women are in games, we
are frequently over sexualized.

00:49:01.850 --> 00:49:04.930
We're always the sidekick
or the damsel in distress,

00:49:04.930 --> 00:49:08.590
and we have huge, giant boobs
with lots of cleavage out.

00:49:08.590 --> 00:49:13.410
And what it is, is 1,000
unconscious signals that

00:49:13.410 --> 00:49:16.890
have been sent to men
saying, this is for you,

00:49:16.890 --> 00:49:18.780
this is not for women.

00:49:18.780 --> 00:49:20.640
